íŸ@39bc50d350b75afa6297ace95409b462d99ff18c89ad5dbe5815dc105a833f89Ÿ˚Title: title: into int
Path: Flags
Content:
``--radix, -r {number}``
: Radix of integer.
``--endian, -e {string}``
: Byte encode endian, available options: native(default), little, big.
``--signed, -s``
: Always treat input number as a signed number.
