íŸ@302a264dd4cc46abee2c37e08344d4ad687893663043dafaa114f1f59193f530⁄¨Title: title: into int
Path: Examples
Content:
Convert string to int in table.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[num]; ['-5'] [4] [1.5]] | into int num


```
Convert string to int.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '2' | into int
2

```
Convert float to int.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 5.9 | into int
5

```
Convert decimal string to int.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '5.9' | into int
5

```
Convert file size to int.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 4KB | into int
4000

```
Convert bool to int.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [false, true] | into int
‚ï≠‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î¨‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚ïÆ
‚îÇ 0 ‚îÇ 0 ‚îÇ
‚îÇ 1 ‚îÇ 1 ‚îÇ
‚ï∞‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î¥‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚ïØ


```
Convert date to int (Unix nanosecond timestamp).
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 1983-04-13T12:09:14.123456789-05:00 | into int
419101754123456789

```
Convert to int from binary data (radix: 2).
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '1101' | into int --radix 2
13

```
Convert to int from hex.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'FF' |  into int --radix 16
255

```
Convert octal string to int.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '0o10132' | into int
4186

```
Convert 0 padded string to int.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '0010132' | into int
10132

```
Convert 0 padded string to int with radix 8.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '0010132' | into int --radix 8
4186

```
Convert binary value to int.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[10] | into int
16

```
Convert binary value to signed int.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[a0] | into int --signed
-96

```
